**No additional runtime dependencies without budget review.** Date formatting uses `Intl.DateTimeFormat`. Form validation is hand-rolled. Focus trapping is hand-rolled (see `useFocusTrap` in Section 5.3). No lodash, no date-fns, no axios.

**Dev dependencies** (not shipped): `vite`, `@vitejs/plugin-react`, `vitest`, `@testing-library/react`, `@testing-library/jest-dom`, `axe-core`, `vitest-axe`, `rollup-plugin-visualizer`, `tailwindcss`, `postcss`, `autoprefixer`.

### 1.4 CI Build & Deployment

1. CI runs `npm ci && npm run build && npm run check:bundle && npm test`
2. `dist/` is a build artifact тАФ **never committed to the repo**
3. Deploy copies `dist/` to the server or builds on the server
4. `web_server.py` includes a startup guard (see Section 2.1) that fails fast if `dist/` is missing

